name: Very Ape
wikiSummary: An up-tempo sweep at the sort of macho pose found in underground rock circles.  Originally titled "Perky New Wave Number".  British techno band The Prodigy sampled the guitar at the beginning for their track "Voodoo People" from the 1995 album "Music for the Jilted Generation
wikiText:
An up-tempo sweep at the sort of macho pose found in underground rock circles.  Originally titled "Perky New Wave Number".
 
 British techno band The Prodigy sampled the guitar at the beginning for their track "Voodoo People" from the 1995 album "Music for the Jilted Generation
